snippet.title: Girlfriend's Sprinter Camper van Build - Ep.1
snippet.description:
The first 1,000 people to use this link will get a 1 month free trial of Skillshare: https://skl.sh/projectamber05211

In this week's video I'm taking you waaay back.
Before Portugal, trip 1 and 2, right back to August last year where Emma had bought a new van to replace her VW T4.
We decided early on that the one van approach wasn't going to work for us, we both enjoy our own time and space, so with the dual van option it gives us that, as well as the freedom to go off on our own, rescue either van, and because they're the same make, even share spare parts.

So this video takes you to the very start of Emma's build, Insulating, or trying to at least, followed up in part 2 by Adding the skylights and Giving the van a new colour scheme.
Subscribe to keep up with Project.Amber:
